  "root_text": {
    "an7.5:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7.5 ",
    "an7.5:0.2": "1. Dhanavagga ",
    "an7.5:0.3": "Saṅkhittadhanasutta ",
    "an7.5:1.1": "“Sattimāni, bhikkhave, dhanāni. ",
    "an7.5:1.2": "Katamāni satta? ",
    "an7.5:1.3": "Saddhādhanaṁ, sīladhanaṁ, hirīdhanaṁ, ottappadhanaṁ, sutadhanaṁ, cāgadhanaṁ, paññādhanaṁ. ",
    "an7.5:1.4": "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, satta dhanānīti. ",
    "an7.5:2.1": "Saddhādhanaṁ sīladhanaṁ, ",
    "an7.5:2.2": "hirī ottappiyaṁ dhanaṁ; ",
    "an7.5:2.3": "Sutadhanañca cāgo ca, ",
    "an7.5:2.4": "paññā ve sattamaṁ dhanaṁ. ",
    "an7.5:3.1": "Yassa ete dhanā atthi, ",
    "an7.5:3.2": "itthiyā purisassa vā; ",
    "an7.5:3.3": "Adaliddoti taṁ āhu, ",
    "an7.5:3.4": "amoghaṁ tassa jīvitaṁ. ",
    "an7.5:4.1": "Tasmā saddhañca sīlañca, ",
    "an7.5:4.2": "Pasādaṁ dhammadassanaṁ; ",
    "an7.5:4.3": "Anuyuñjetha medhāvī, ",
    "an7.5:4.4": "Saraṁ buddhāna sāsanan”ti. ",
    "an7.5:4.5": "Pañcamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an7.5:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 7.5 ",
    "an7.5:0.2": "1. Wealth ",
    "an7.5:0.3": "Wealth in Brief ",
    "an7.5:1.1": "“Mendicants, there are these seven kinds of wealth. ",
    "an7.5:1.2": "What seven? ",
    "an7.5:1.3": "The wealth of faith, ethics, conscience, prudence, learning, generosity, and wisdom. ",
    "an7.5:1.4": "These are the seven kinds of wealth. ",
    "an7.5:2.1": "Faith and ethical conduct are kinds of wealth, ",
    "an7.5:2.2": "as are conscience and prudence, ",
    "an7.5:2.3": "learning and generosity, ",
    "an7.5:2.4": "and wisdom is the seventh kind of wealth. ",
    "an7.5:3.1": "When a woman or man ",
    "an7.5:3.2": "has these kinds of wealth, ",
    "an7.5:3.3": "they’re said to be prosperous, ",
    "an7.5:3.4": "their life is not in vain. ",
    "an7.5:4.1": "So let the wise devote themselves ",
    "an7.5:4.2": "to faith, ethical behavior, ",
    "an7.5:4.3": "confidence, and insight into the teaching, ",
    "an7.5:4.4": "remembering the instructions of the Buddhas.” "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "an7.5:4.4": "Saraṁ → varaṁ (mr) "
  },
